00:20:30.630 --> 00:20:32.420
"Vous êtes tous virés."

00:20:33.720 --> 00:20:36.220
Oimo... kaashii...

00:20:36.930 --> 00:20:38.930
Comment avez-vous...

00:20:39.540 --> 00:20:41.050
